### üîê Privacy & Security

#### Is my data private?
**Absolutely!** Your privacy is our top priority:

‚úÖ Files **never permanently stored** on our servers  
‚úÖ Cloud conversions **immediately deleted** after download  
‚úÖ Local conversions stay **entirely on your device**  
‚úÖ No account or personal information required  
‚úÖ Anonymous authentication only  
‚úÖ HTTPS encryption for all transfers  

See our [Privacy Policy](PRIVACY_POLICY.md) for details.

#### Where are my files stored?
- **Original files**: Only on your device
- **Converted files**: Saved to your device's Documents folder
- **During cloud conversion**: Temporarily uploaded, immediately deleted after

#### Can you see my files?
No! We use anonymous authentication and don't have access to your file contents.

