### üåü Tips & Tricks

#### Best practices for conversions
- Use local conversions when possible (faster, offline)
- Keep files under 100 MB for best results
- Ensure stable internet for cloud conversions
- Check converted files before deleting originals

#### Fastest conversions
These formats convert locally (super fast):
- Image to PDF: JPG/PNG/HEIC ‚Üí PDF
- Image format changes: JPG ‚Üî PNG ‚Üî HEIC
- Text to PDF: TXT ‚Üí PDF

#### Battery-saving tips
- Use local conversions when possible
- Convert multiple files at once (coming soon!)
- Use WiFi instead of cellular for cloud conversions

